      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a major restoration project or a source for spare parts. The exterior has extensive rust damage on the frame and lower body panels, alongside significant paint peeling and several large dents. Mechanically, the car is not currently reliable; the engine runs roughly and requires immediate attention, and the suspension is heavily worn. Inside, the cabin shows its age with torn seats, a cracked dashboard, and several electrical components that are no longer operational. Expect to put in considerable work to bring this vehicle back to a drivable state.",
